title: AI study of risk factors in type 1 diabetes

title_detail.value: AI study of risk factors in type 1 diabetes

summary: In combination with conventional statistical methods, artificial intelligence (AI) has now been used in a study of risk factors in type 1 diabetes. The objective was to identify the most important indicators of elevated risk for cardiovascular disease and death.
